text: I don’t see enough people interested in business issues here. I’m going to sign out. Anyone who wants to talk about business or design, please see my web site - <http://www.kryptodesign.com|www.kryptodesign.com> - and contact me: <mailto:david@dsiegel.com|david@dsiegel.com>

As a guess - is it possible people are interested in business issues, but many of the firms engaged in this project have their own commercial aspirations that they may not want to talk too much about?  If that's on people's minds - maybe we should set some rules for the channel that would allow some sort of useful dialog
<@U0KM0C3M3>: agreed and noticed. Thanks for reminder. Rules should be set in dialog.
